{
  "text": "A semistructured interview guide was developed to explore the following topics: experiences of falls/near-falls; perceptions of change in falls and/or near-falls type and frequency since adolescence; physical health consequences of falls/near-falls; and psychosocial health consequences of falls/near-falls. To clarify responses and identify examples, the interviewer rephrased the questions and asked followup questions if required [CITATION_1] . The interview also explored participants' experiences of health service access and utilisation. This latter data has been reported elsewhere [CITATION_2] .",
